videos.description: AJ Dillon burst through the pile for a 22-yard touchdown to get the Eagles on the board.
videos.headline: Boston College scores first with rushing TD

videos.description: AJ Dillon turns on the spin cycle for the touchdown to pad the Eagles' lead over the Orange.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Boston College's Dillon spins into end zone for TD) 2017/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Boston College's Dillon spins into end zone for TD

videos.description: Rex Culpepper throws a lateral pass that is almost intercepted, Eagles' Will Harris sees the live ball on the ground and picks it up for a 30-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Syracuse confusion leads to Boston College TD

videos.description: Jeff Smith bursts and runs away from the Orange defense to take it all the way into the end zone for a 64-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Boston College's Smith streaks for 64-yard TD

videos.description: Rex Culpepper connects with an open Ervin Phillips in the back of the end zone for a 17-yard touchdown to narrow the Orange's deficit.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Culpepper finds Phillip for TD

videos.description: Surrounded by Syracuse defenders, AJ Dillon muscles his way into the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Boston College's Dillon gets third rushing TD

videos.description: Darius Wade passes to Travis Levy who zigzags through the Orange defense on his way to the end zone for a 46-yard touchdown for the Eagles.
videos.headline: Boston College's Levy weaves through defenders for TD
